  <entry>
    <title>Ros PY文件执行不通过</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2021/03/30/ros%20py%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E5%8D%A1%E6%AD%BB%E4%B8%8D%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2021/03/30/ros%20py%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E5%8D%A1%E6%AD%BB%E4%B8%8D%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87/</id>
    <published>2021-03-30T06:55:49.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-03-30T12:09:02.798Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><h2 id="python文件-rosrun执行不通过"><a href="#python文件-rosrun执行不通过" class="headerlink" title="python文件 rosrun执行不通过"></a>python文件 rosrun执行不通过</h2><p>在script 文件夹中，在ros终端中始终是卡死，然后提示代码有错误，检查了好多遍没有发现错误<br>原因是因为在python文件的头部加入</p><figure class="highlight d"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs d"><span class="hljs-meta">#!/usr/bin/env python</span><br># -*- coding: utf-<span class="hljs-number">8</span> -*-<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>这段话是来表明你的问价是一个可以执行的python脚本程序，不然是无法执行的。</p><p>然后再记录一下如何创建自己的msg包<br>首先在你的元功能包中与src同级目录下创建msg文件夹，然后在该文件夹下创建你要写的“文件名.msg”，里面写你的类似于struct的结构体文件。</p><p>在在package.xml中添加功能包依赖 </p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">build_depend</span>&gt;</span>message_generation<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">build_depend</span>&gt;</span> <br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">exec_depend</span>&gt;</span>message_runtime<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">exec_depend</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">build_export_depend</span>&gt;</span>message_generation<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">build_export_depend</span>&gt;</span>  <br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>然后在在CMakeLists.txt添加编译选项<br>在find_package(),下面是我的find_package()</p><figure class="highlight isbl"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs isbl"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">find_package</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">catkin</span> <span class="hljs-variable">REQUIRED</span> <span class="hljs-variable">COMPONENTS</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function">  <span class="hljs-variable">geometry_msgs</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function">  <span class="hljs-variable">roscpp</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function">  <span class="hljs-variable">rospy</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function">  <span class="hljs-variable">std_msgs</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function">  <span class="hljs-variable">turtlesim</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function">  <span class="hljs-variable">message_generation</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function">)</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>在add_message_files() 以及generate_messages()中添加如下内容</p><figure class="highlight isbl"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs isbl"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">add_message_files</span>(</span><br><span class="hljs-function">   <span class="hljs-variable">FILES</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function">   <span class="hljs-variable">Person.msg</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"> )</span><br> <br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">generate_messages</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">DEPENDENCIES</span> <span class="hljs-variable">std_msgs</span>)</span><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>然后再在catkin中添加如下内容</p><figure class="highlight autoit"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs autoit">catkin_package(<br><span class="hljs-meta">#  INCLUDE_DIRS <span class="hljs-meta-keyword">include</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#  LIBRARIES test_pkg</span><br>   CATKIN_DEPENDS roscpp rospy std_msgs  geometry_msgs message_runtime turtlesim<br>  <span class="hljs-meta"># DEPENDS system_lib</span><br>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p><strong><em>python 文件还要修改catkin_install_python中的scripts/文件名.py文件</em></strong></p><p>生成新项目步骤</p><ol><li>创建文件夹<figure class="highlight arcade"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs arcade">mkdir -p ~<span class="hljs-regexp">/catkin_ws/</span>src <br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li><li>cd至src文件夹内 <figure class="highlight arcade"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs arcade">cd ~<span class="hljs-regexp">/catkin_ws/</span>src<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li><li>将次文件声明为工作空间<figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">catkin_init_workspace</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li><li>返回你创建的初始文件件进行编译<figure class="highlight arcade"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs arcade">cd ~<span class="hljs-regexp">/catkin_ws/</span><br>catkin_make<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li><li>将工作环境添加到环境变量中<figure class="highlight arduino"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs arduino">source devel/<span class="hljs-built_in">setup</span>.bash<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li><li>创建功能包<figure class="highlight arcade"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs arcade">cd ~<span class="hljs-regexp">/catkin_ws/</span>src<br>catkin_create_pkg test_pkg std_msgs rospy roscpp<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li><li>再次编译环境<figure class="highlight gradle"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs gradle">cd ~/catkin_ws <br>catkin_make <br><span class="hljs-keyword">source</span> ~<span class="hljs-regexp">/catkin_ws/</span>devel/setup.bash<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li><li>生成install文件<figure class="highlight cmake"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cmake">catkin_make <span class="hljs-keyword">install</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
